==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Splutter
<hw>Splut"ter</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A confused noise, as of hasty
speaking.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

